{"tid":2278351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商人涉冒警騙少女口交 今提堂不准保釋　","createTime":"2020-11-09T05:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T10:13:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"b03ce25f08df123ae8c3df2d6301b63c03188b0d","tid":2278351,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"27歲生果進出口商人今年8月在交友網站認識14歲少女，其後少女透露男友在沙田區犯事被捕，商人涉自稱沙田警區高級督察，訛稱可以幫助少女，繼而帶少女到時鐘酒店要求少女替他口交，最終事件曝光。涉案商人被控冒充公職人員及非禮兩罪，案件今於西九龍裁判法院提堂，並押後至周三（11日）再訊，以待進行認人手續。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請，還柙候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/UEHWVYTZT5FJ7EZLQWGQWSZMGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FUEHWVYTZT5FJ7EZLQWGQWSZMGU%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=f596476f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FUEHWVYTZT5FJ7EZLQWGQWSZMGU%2F&h=0e49c187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/UEHWVYTZT5FJ7EZLQWGQWSZMGU/</a>"},{"pid":"f20131f936c5dc72b0fff761d96fe28d9c4a9342","tid":2278351,"uid":290118,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"伙記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f0f8e3ab200a284f7dc049614daac02945cc8d","tid":2278351,"uid":58841,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"有人唔扮扮狗係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad649887b2e5b3ba14e95404a4a3afdd2962b124","tid":2278351,"uid":204539,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">走apple水貨 = 生果進出口商人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e2d32292d49664dd71092c893bf034258858b6","tid":2278351,"uid":238214,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:54:23.000Z"